ightning bolts."},{"version":"yellow","text":"A sensitive POK\u00e9\u00ad MON that easily becomes sad or angry. Every time its mood changes, it charges power."},{"version":"gold","text":"It concentrates the weak electric charges emitted by its cells and launches wicked lightning bolts."},{"version":"silver","text":"Every hair on its body starts to stand sharply on end if it becomes charged with electricity."},{"version":"crystal","text":"The negatively charged ions generated in its fur create a constant sparking noise."},{"version":"ruby","text":"JOLTEON\u2019s cells generate a low level of electricity. This power is amplified by the static electricity of its fur, enabling the POK\u00e9MON to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"JOLTEON\u2019s cells generate a low level of electricity. This power is amplified by the static electricity of its fur, enabling the POK\u00e9MON to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Its cells generate weak power that is amplified by its fur\u2019s static electricity to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles."},{"version":"firered","text":"If it is angered or startled, the fur all over its body bristles like sharp needles that pierce foes."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10,000-volt lightning bolts."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It controls 10,000-volt power and can raise all the fur on its body as if it were sharp needles."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It controls 10,000-volt power and can raise all the fur on its body as if it were sharp needles."},{"version":"platinum","text":"If agitated, it uses electricity to straighten out its fur and launch it in small bunches."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It concentrates the weak electric charges emitted by its cells and launches wicked lightning bolts."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Every hair on its body starts to stand sharply on end if it becomes charged with electricity."},{"version":"black","text":"If agitated, it uses electricity to straighten out its fur and launch it in small bunches."},{"version":"white","text":"If agitated, it uses electricity to straighten out its fur and launch it in small bunches."},{"version":"black-2","text":"By storing electricity in its body, it can shoot its bristlelike fur like a barrage of missiles."},{"version":"white-2","text":"By storing electricity in its body, it can shoot its bristlelike fur like a barrage of missiles."},{"version":"x","text":"Every hair on its body starts to stand sharply on end if it becomes charged with electricity."},{"version":"y","text":"It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10,000-volt lightning bolts."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Jolteon\u2019s cells generate a low level of electricity. This power is amplified by the static electricity of its fur, enabling the Pok\u00e9mon to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Jolteon\u2019s cells generate a low level of electricity. This power is amplified by the static electricity of its fur, enabling the Pok\u00e9mon to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles."},{"version":"sun","text":"They send out electrical charges of about 10,000 volts. Because they are high-strung, it can be difficult to grow close to them."},{"version":"moon","text":"When its fur stands on end, that\u2019s a sign it\u2019s about to give off a jolt of electricity. Take care, as sometimes lightning strikes next to it, too."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Its lungs contain an organ that creates electricity. The crackling sound of electricity can be heard when it exhales."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its fur stands on end, becoming like needles it fires at enemies. Once they\u2019re weakened, it finishes them off with a 10,000 volt shock."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"A sensitive Pok\u00e9mon that easily becomes sad or angry. Every time its mood changes, it charges power."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"A sensitive Pok\u00e9mon that easily becomes sad or angry. Every time its mood changes, it charges power."},{"version":"sword","text":"If it is angered or startled, the fur all over its body bristles like sharp needles that pierce foes."},{"version":"shield","text":"It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10,000-volt lightning bolts."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Bristles its fur into sharp, needlelike points when enraged. One can hear electricity crackle in its breath when it exhales."}],"evo":{"name":"eevee","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"vaporeon","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"water-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"jolteon","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"thunder-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"flareon","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"fire-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"espeon","l